GET USED TO STAYING HERE.

17:53.772 --> 17:56.175
HEY! MIRANDA!

17:56.175 --> 17:57.376
JOSH...

17:57.376 --> 17:58.577
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

17:58.977 --> 17:59.778
WHAT'S YOUR PROBLEM?

18:00.179 --> 18:01.380
YOU ARE.

18:01.380 --> 18:03.382
WELL, IF YOU GOT SOMETHING TO
SAY, THEN WHY DON'T YOU SAY IT?

18:03.382 --> 18:07.386
YOU KNOW, THERE
ARE SOME THINGS THAT DON'T
ADD UP ABOUT YOU, BEN.

18:07.386 --> 18:10.589
I'M GONNA FIGURE YOU
OUT, AND WHEN I DO, MIRANDA AND

18:10.589 --> 18:12.591
EVERYONE ELSE IN THIS COMMUNITY
IS GOING TO UNDERSTAND WHAT

18:12.591 --> 18:14.193
YOU'RE TRYING TO DO TO US.

18:14.193 --> 18:16.195
I'M NOT TRYING TO DO
ANYTHING TO THIS COMMUNITY.

18:16.595 --> 18:19.798
NOW, AS FOR MIRANDA, I'M
STARTING TO LOSE PATIENCE WITH

18:19.798 --> 18:22.201
HAVING TO TELL YOU THAT
SHE DECIDES WHO SHE'S WITH.

18:22.601 --> 18:25.003
