THERE, FIGHTING FOR ME.

19:05.844 --> 19:10.249
YEAH, YOU'RE WORTH FIGHTING FOR.

19:14.653 --> 19:17.055
HOW DOES THAT FEEL?

19:17.055 --> 19:19.458
LIKE BRAND NEW.

19:59.631 --> 20:02.034
SEE, I TOLD YOU NEW
HOPE WOULD GROW ON YOU.

20:02.034 --> 20:04.436
YEAH, I MUST HAVE.

20:04.436 --> 20:07.239
