20:09.241 --> 20:11.643
AND WHAT'S SO GREAT
ABOUT YOUR WORLD, ANYWAY?

20:11.643 --> 20:13.645
OH, EVERYTHING.

20:14.046 --> 20:20.052
THAI FOOD AND DANCE
CLUBS, OCEANS, CARS...

20:20.452 --> 20:24.456
