ANY TROUBLE, IS THERE?

20:52.884 --> 20:54.486
NO, NO, THERE'S NO TROUBLE.

20:54.486 --> 20:56.088
I JUST...

20:56.088 --> 20:58.090
WANT TO TALK TO HIM IS ALL.

20:58.090 --> 20:59.691
CAN WE HAVE A MINUTE?

21:00.092 --> 21:01.293
WELL, I'M KIND OF BUSY, BUT...

21:01.293 --> 21:04.896
YEAH.

21:08.500 --> 21:10.902
IT'S ABOUT THE
WORLD OUTSIDE THE WALL.

21:10.902 --> 21:13.305
I KNOW.

21:13.305 --> 21:16.108
