YOU, I WOULDN'T HAVE COME ALONE.

21:18.510 --> 21:21.313
I'VE GOT SOMETHING TO SHOW YOU.

21:21.313 --> 21:24.116
COME WITH ME.

21:24.116 --> 21:26.918
PLEASE?

21:28.520 --> 21:30.122
ALL RIGHT.

21:35.327 --> 21:36.928
LOOK, MIRANDA, I'M
GOING TO BE BACK IN A MINUTE.

21:36.928 --> 21:39.731
I'M GONNA GO WITH ZANDER, OKAY?

21:45.737 --> 21:46.938
