21:46.938 --> 21:48.140
NO, YOU'RE NOT GETTING
A BREAK UNTIL YOU'RE FINISHED.

21:48.140 --> 21:49.741
HEY.

21:49.741 --> 21:51.343
WE FOUND OUR FRIEND'S CAR.

21:51.743 --> 21:53.345
FOUND THAT, AND
THE TRUCK THAT HIT HIM.

21:53.345 --> 21:55.347
