YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

21:55.347 --> 21:56.948
YOU'RE LYING.

21:56.948 --> 22:00.152
IT WAS MY HUSBAND'S TRUCK.

22:00.152 --> 22:03.355
IT HAPPENED OVER BY
WHERE LEWISTON USED TO BE.

22:03.755 --> 22:06.558
THAT WHOLE AREA SPOOKS ME.

22:06.558 --> 22:07.359
YEAH?

22:07.759 --> 22:08.960
WHY'S THAT?

22:08.960 --> 22:10.962
IT'S JUST A
STORY THAT FOLKS TELL,

22:10.962 --> 22:12.964
BUT I KNOW THERE'S TRUTH TO IT.

22:12.964 --> 22:14.566
WELL, IT USED TO BE
AN ABANDONED MINING TOWN.

22:14.966 --> 22:16.968
YEAH, WELL, I DON'T REMEMBER
SEEING ANY TOWN THERE.

22:16.968 --> 22:18.570
EXACTLY.

22:18.570 --> 22:19.771
ONE DAY THE WHOLE PLACE JUST...

22:20.172 --> 22:22.174
DISAPPEARED.

22:22.174 --> 22:25.377
JUST LIKE BRENNAN.

22:25.377 --> 22:27.379
YOU KNOW, YOU BETTER
BE TELLING US THE TRUTH.

22:27.779 --> 22:30.182
BECAUSE IF OUR FRIEND
DOESN'T SHOW UP SOON...

22:30.582 --> 22:34.986
I'M COMING BACK
FOR YOU AND YOUR HUSBAND.

22:38.990 --> 22:41.393
I FOUND THESE A FEW YEARS BACK.

22:41.393 --> 22:45.797
THAT'S
WHEN I KNEW THAT EVERYTHING
THE ELDERS TOLD US WAS A LIE.

22:45.797 --> 22:49.801
SEE?

22:49.801 --> 22:52.204
HERE ARE THESE PICTURES.

22:52.604 --> 22:55.407
ALL DIFFERENT PLACES, AND...

22:55.807 --> 22:59.811
AND PEOPLE WITH
STRANGE COSTUMES IN THEM.

22:59.811 --> 23:03.415
SEE, WHEN I SAW THOSE MARKS
ON YOUR ARM, THAT'S WHEN I KNEW

23:03.415 --> 23:06.618
YOU WERE FROM OUT THERE,
THAT THESE PLACES WERE REAL.

23:07.018 --> 23:09.421
I'VE DREAMT ABOUT
THESE PLACES FOR YEARS.

23:09.421 --> 23:13.024
MAYBE IT'S CRAZY,
BUT I EVEN DREAMED THAT
I COULD GO OUT THERE MYSELF.

23:13.024 --> 23:17.429
I'LL TELL YOU
WHAT, ZANDER, YOU GET ME
OUT OF THIS TOWN, YOU CAN.

23:17.429 --> 23:21.032
THERE'S A WHOLE WORLD
OUT THERE FOR YOU TO EXPLORE.

23:26.238 --> 23:29.441
COUNCIL FINDS OUT ABOUT
YOU, YOU MIGHT DISAPPEAR.

23:29.441 --> 23:30.642
HEY, YOU KNOW WHAT?

23:30.642 --> 23:33.044
MIRANDA TALKED ABOUT
PEOPLE DISAPPEARING.

23:33.445 --> 23:39.050
I SOMETIMES HAVE
TO TAKE PEOPLE TO COUNCIL
WHEN THEY'VE LOST THEIR WAY.

23:39.050 --> 23:41.052
YOU KNOW, DIDN'T
BELIEVE, OR EVEN WORSE,

23:41.052 --> 23:43.054
SPOKE OUT AGAINST THE TOWN CODE.

23:43.054 --> 23:45.056
NOW COUNCIL CLAIMS THEY'VE
DISAPPEARED, BUT I KNOW BETTER.

23:45.457 --> 23:47.859
THEY TOLD THEM THE WAY OUT OF
TOWN WAS THROUGH THE BASEMENT.

23:47.859 --> 23:49.861
BUT THERE'S NO WAY OUT.

23:49.861 --> 23:52.264
THEY JUST WALKED INTO THE
BASEMENT OF THE TOWN HALL AND

23:52.264 --> 23:53.865
NEVER CAME OUT.

23:53.865 --> 23:55.867
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

23:55.867 --> 23:57.469
WELL, I DON'T
KNOW WHAT'S DOWN THERE,

23:57.469 --> 23:59.070
BUT I GOT A LOOK ONE TIME.

23:59.070 --> 24:01.072
IT'S... IT'S...
IT'S ALL METAL AND...

24:01.473 --> 24:03.475
AND LIGHTS, AND GLASS...

24:03.875 --> 24:05.877
WELL, THAT'S GOTTA
BE THE FORCE FIELD GENERATOR.

24:05.877 --> 24:09.080
YOU KNOW WHAT?

24:09.080 --> 24:10.682
WE GOTTA FIND A WAY OUT OF HERE.

24:10.682 --> 24:12.684
THERE'S GOTTA BE A
WAY TO STOP THAT FORCE FIELD.

24:12.684 --> 24:14.286
WELL, THERE ARE
OTHER PEOPLE WE CAN TRUST,

24:14.686 --> 24:15.887
PEOPLE WHO THINK LIKE ME.

24:15.887 --> 24:17.489
ONE OF THEM
MIGHT BE ABLE TO HELP.

24:17.489 --> 24:18.690
YOU WAIT HERE.

24:18.690 --> 24:21.092
I'LL BE BACK.

24:30.702 --> 24:33.505
WONDER IF I MIGHT HAVE
A WORD WITH YOU, ZANDER.

24:33.505 --> 24:37.108
THAT IS,
OF COURSE, UNLESS YOU'RE
HERE ON OFFICIAL BUSINESS.

24:37.509 --> 24:40.312
HUH, WHAT IS IT?

24:40.312 --> 24:41.913
YOU'RE SUPPOSED
TO BE A PEACEKEEPER.

24:42.314 --> 24:44.316
YOU'RE SUPPOSED TO
UPHOLD TOWN COUNCIL'S WILL.

24:44.316 --> 24:46.718
I DO.

24:47.118 --> 24:53.124
YOU'RE HELPING THE OUTSIDER.

24:53.124 --> 24:55.527
EVERYTHING THEY
TOLD US WAS A LIE, JOSH.

24:55.927 --> 24:57.529
WE CAN GET OUTSIDE THE WALL.

24:57.529 --> 24:58.730
HE'S GOING TO HELP US.

24:58.730 --> 25:00.332
I'LL GET THE OTHERS.

25:11.943 --> 25:13.545
WE NEED ANSWERS, ADAM.

25:13.945 --> 25:15.146
WELL, I'VE FOUND SOME,

25:15.146 --> 25:17.949
BUT RIGHT NOW THEY
DON'T MAKE A LOT OF SENSE.

25:17.949 --> 25:19.150
TRY US.

25:19.150 --> 25:21.553
WELL, ALBERT MARCUS,
IS A WALKING CONTRADICTION.

25:21.553 --> 25:25.557
HE WAS A SCIENTIST
BUT HE HATED MODERN SOCIETY.

25:25.557 --> 25:29.160
NOW, HIS DREAM WAS TO CREATE
A SELF-SUFFICIENT COMMUNITY

25:29.160 --> 25:33.565
THAT WAS FREE OF THE NEGATIVE
INFLUENCES OF THE OUTSIDE WORLD.

25:33.565 --> 25:35.567
YOU CAN'T JUST DECIDE
TO NOT BE INFLUENCED.

25:35.567 --> 25:36.768
WELL, NOW, WAIT.

25:37.168 --> 25:38.370
MAYBE YOU CAN.

25:38.370 --> 25:40.372
SEE, ONE OF THE PROJECTS
HE WAS WORKING ON WAS A...

25:40.772 --> 25:41.973
IT'S KIND OF
AN ELECTRONIC BUBBLE.

25:42.374 --> 25:44.776
IT WAS AN IMPENETRABLE
FORCE FIELD THAT HE COULD PLACE

25:44.776 --> 25:46.778
OVER AN ENTIRE TOWN.

25:46.778 --> 25:48.780
OH, I DON'T LIKE
THE SOUNDS OF THIS.

25:48.780 --> 25:52.384
SO THIS TOWN THAT ALFRED
MARCUS HAD HIS EYE ON WAS WHAT?

25:52.384 --> 25:54.786
THIRTY MILES WEST OF EDGARSTOWN?

25:54.786 --> 25:56.788
EXACTLY.

25:56.788 --> 25:58.790
LEWISTON.

25:58.790 --> 26:01.192
THAT'S RIGHT AROUND
WHERE BRENNAN DISAPPEARED.

26:01.593 --> 26:04.796
WE'RE ON IT, ADAM.

26:15.206 --> 26:16.808
ZANDER'S DEAD.

26:16.808 --> 26:19.210
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

26:19.210 --> 26:23.615
BEN GILBERT KILLED ZANDER.

26:23.615 --> 26:25.216
HE MURDERED HIM WITH HIS KNIFE.

26:25.216 --> 26:27.218
I SAW THE WHOLE
THING WITH MY OWN EYES.

26:27.218 --> 26:28.820
NO.

26:29.220 --> 26:32.424
ZANDER WAS GOING TO
TURN HIM IN TO TOWN COUNCIL.

26:32.424 --> 26:35.226
HE WOULDN'T HAVE DONE THAT.

26:35.226 --> 26:36.828
I TOLD YOU I SAW IT.

26:36.828 --> 26:42.834
YOU DON'T EVEN KNOW
ANYTHING ABOUT HIM, DO YOU?

26:47.238 --> 26:48.440
OKAY, HEY...

26:48.440 --> 26:50.041
MIRANDA, LISTEN.

26:50.041 --> 26:51.242
HEY.

26:51.643 --> 26:53.244
NOW THEY'RE GOING TO
WANT TO TALK TO YOU, OKAY,

26:53.244 --> 26:55.647
BECAUSE YOU WERE WITH HIM.

26:56.047 --> 26:58.450
BUT I CAN PROTECT
YOU, ALL RIGHT?

26:58.850 --> 27:02.854
YOU JUST HAVE
TO DO THE RIGHT THING.

27:02.854 --> 27:09.260
OKAY? -OKAY.

27:30.882 --> 27:34.886
THIS IS RIGHT AROUND WHERE THE
LEWISTON TOWN LIMITS WOULD BE.

27:34.886 --> 27:36.087
CRUISE AROUND,
SEE WHAT WE CAN FIND.

27:38.089 --> 27:42.494
BRENNAN? BRENNAN?

27:42.494 --> 27:44.496
BRENNAN.

27:44.896 --> 27:47.298
YEAH. YEAH, I'M UP HERE.

27:47.298 --> 27:49.701
THE WHOLE TOWN'S
LOOKING FOR YOU.

27:49.701 --> 27:52.103
IT'S NOT SAFE HERE.

27:59.310 --> 28:00.912
WHERE WE GOING?

28:00.912 --> 28:02.113
DON'T WORRY. JUST COME WITH ME.

28:02.514 --> 28:04.916
WHAT?
-COME WITH ME.

28:05.316 --> 28:08.520
MIRANDA, COME HERE.

28:08.520 --> 28:10.522
YOU SHOULDN'T HAVE
KILLED ZANDER, BRENNAN.

28:10.522 --> 28:11.723
HE WOULDN'T HAVE HURT YOU.

28:11.723 --> 28:12.924
WHAT?

28:12.924 --> 28:14.526
I DIDN'T KILL ANYBODY.

28:14.526 --> 28:16.127
TAKE HIM.

28:46.558 --> 28:50.562
YOU MADE YOURSELF
A BIG MISTAKE... BEN.

28:50.962 --> 28:52.163
PICK HIM UP.

28:52.163 --> 28:54.566
LET'S GO.

28:57.769 --> 29:01.773
MIRANDA! MIRANDA!

29:01.773 --> 29:04.576
MIRANDA!

29:15.353 --> 29:18.156
LET'S PROCEED.

29:18.156 --> 29:20.959
BEN GILBERT, YOU ARE CHARGED
WITH A CRIME NEVER BEFORE SEEN

29:20.959 --> 29:23.361
IN NEW HOPE, THE
MURDER OF ANOTHER PERSON.

29:23.361 --> 29:26.965
OUR BELOVED ZANDER DELASSANDRO.

29:26.965 --> 29:29.768
ZANDER WAS TRYING TO HELP ME,
SO WHY WOULD I WANT TO KILL HIM?

29:30.168 --> 29:32.971
